<div class='questionText'>
<a href="/questions/923602-is-there-anything-inappropriate-for-young">Is there anything inappropriate for young readers in this book? 
My young DD is passionate about mathematics and is dying to read this book, and prefers to read the original versus the young readers version. She reads at a high school level. Thank you!</a>
</div>
